modal\" role=\"button\" tabindex=\"0\"><svg aria-hidden=\"true\" class=\"ico-feedback\"><use xlink:href=\"#ico-feedback\"></use></svg><span class=\"zDocsFeedbackButtonText\"> Feedback</span></span></div></div><div class=\"zDocsTopicActionsMobile\"><button aria-label=\"Show topic actions\" data-toggle=\"dropdown\" id=\"zDocsTopicActionsMobile\"><svg aria-hidden=\"true\" class=\"ico-ellipsis-h\"><use xlink:href=\"#ico-ellipsis-h\"></use></svg></button><div class=\"dropdown-menu zDocsDropdownMenu zDocsTopicActionsMobileDropdown dropdown-menu-right\"></div></div><div style=\"flex-basis: 100%; height: 0px;\"></div><ul class=\"zDocsTopicPageDetails\"><li class=\"zDocsTopicPageDate css-cinqea\">Last Updated<span class=\"css-cinqea\">Jan 19, 2024</span></li><li class=\"zDocsAiTopicSummaryDetailsItem\"><button class=\"zDocsAiTopicSummaryButton\"><svg aria-hidden=\"true\" class=\"ico-topic-summary\"><use xlink:href=\"#ico-topic-summary\"></use></svg>Summarize</button></li><li class=\"spacer\" role=\"presentation\"></li><div class=\"zDocsLabelWrapper\"><ul><li class=\"zDocsLabel\"><a aria-describedby=\"hyperLinkFacetsTooltip\" class=\"css-ettsdk\" data-tooltip-content=\"Search all site by tag: Uniface\" data-tooltip-id=\"hyperLinkFacetsTooltip\" href=\"/de-DE/search?labelkey=prod_uniface\" stylesprops=\"[object Object]\"><svg aria-label=\"Tag\" class=\"ico-tag\" role=\"img\"><use xlink:href=\"#ico-tag\"></use></svg>Uniface</a></li><li class=\"zDocsLabel\"><a aria-describedby=\"hyperLinkFacetsTooltip\" class=\"css-ettsdk\" data-tooltip-content=\"Search all site by tag: 10.4\" data-tooltip-id=\"hyperLinkFacetsTooltip\" href=\"/de-DE/search?labelkey=uniface_10.4\" stylesprops=\"[object Object]\"><svg aria-label=\"Tag\" class=\"ico-tag\" role=\"img\"><use xlink:href=\"#ico-tag\"></use></svg>10.4</a></li></ul></div></ul></header><div class=\"zDocsTopicPageBody\" data-prismjs-copy=\"Copy\" data-prismjs-copy-error=\"Copy failed! Use Ctrl + C instead.\" data-prismjs-copy-success=\"Copied!\"><div class=\"zDocsTopicPageBodyContent\" dir=\"ltr\"><div id=\"zDocsAiSummaryContaineruniface_104sxb1705569063728.html\"></div><div><article class=\"hascomments\" data-page=\"bundle:uniface_104/enus/sxb1705569063728.html\" id=\"bundle:uniface_104/enus/sxb1705569063728.html\"><main role=\"main\"><article aria-labelledby=\"ariaid-title1\" class=\"dita\" id=\"xkf1665702809265\" role=\"article\">\n<h1 class=\"title topictitle1\" id=\"ariaid-title1\">\n                             \n Working with Help Texts \n      \n   </h1>\n<div class=\"body taskbody\"><p class=\"shortdesc\">Define help texts to create large blocks of text that can be displayed in a Uniface help window.\n </p>\n<section class=\"section context\" id=\"xkf1665702809265__context_w3829ab1b5b1_w3830ab1b5_w3831ab1\">\n<div class=\"note note note_note\" id=\"xkf1665702809265__note_w3832ab1b5b1b1_w3833ab1b5b1_w3834ab1b5_w3835ab1\"><span class=\"note__title\">Note:</span> Help texts are provided for backward compatibility. They are not recommended for modern applications.</div>\n</section>\n<section><ol class=\"ol steps\"><li class=\"li step stepexpand\" id=\"xkf1665702809265__li_d6209e1_d6210e1_d6211e1\">\n<span class=\"ph cmd\">Open the help text editor:\n </span>\n<ol class=\"ol substeps\" type=\"a\">\n<li class=\"li substep substepexpand\" id=\"xkf1665702809265__li_d6212e1_d6213e1_d6214e1\">\n<span class=\"ph cmd\">Choose <span class=\"ph menucascade\"><span class=\"ph uicontrol\">More Editors</span><abbr title=\"and then\"> &gt; </abbr><span class=\"ph uicontrol\">Help Texts</span></span>. </span>\n</li>\n<li class=\"li substep substepexpand\" id=\"xkf1665702809265__li_d6215e1_d6216e1_d6217e1\">\n<span class=\"ph cmd\" id=\"xkf1665702809265__p_d12986e1_d12987e1_d12988e1\">Select or create the Message Library in\n                     which you want to store the help texts.</span>\n<div class=\"itemgroup info\">The object editor is now opened.</div>\n</li>\n</ol>\n</li><li class=\"li step stepexpand\" id=\"xkf1665702809265__li_d6218e1_d6219e1_d6220e1\">\n<span class=\"ph cmd\">To create a help text:\n </span>\n<ol class=\"ol substeps\" type=\"a\">\n<li class=\"li substep substepexpand\" id=\"xkf1665702809265__li_d6221e1_d6222e1_d6223e1\">\n<span class=\"ph cmd\">Click <span class=\"ph uicontrol\">New</span> and enter the <span class=\"ph uicontrol\">Help Name</span>, <span class=\"ph uicontrol\">Language</span>, and optional <span class=\"ph uicontrol\">Description</span>.\n </span>\n<div class=\"itemgroup info\">\n<div class=\"note note note_note\" id=\"xkf1665702809265__p_d12989e1_d12990e1_d12991e1\"><span class=\"note__title\">Note:</span>  Each help text must have a\n                        unique name. It cannot use the same name as a message because messages and\n                        help texts are stored in the same library. </div>\n</div>\n</li>\n<li class=\"li substep substepexpand\" id=\"xkf1665702809265__li_d6224e1_d6225e1_d6226e1\">\n<span class=\"ph cmd\">Enter the text in the <span class=\"ph uicontrol\">Text</span> field.\n </span>\n</li>\n<li class=\"li substep substepexpand\" id=\"xkf1665702809265__li_d6227e1_d6228e1_d6229e1\">\n<span class=\"ph cmd\" id=\"xkf1665702809265__p_d12992e1_d12993e1_d12994e1\">Optionally, set the <span class=\"ph uicontrol\">Window\n                        Geometry</span> to define the position and size of the help window. </span>\n<div class=\"itemgroup info\">\n<p class=\"p\">To define the position, set the <span class=\"ph uicontrol\">Left</span> and\n                           <span class=\"ph uicontrol\">Top</span> properties. To define the dimensions, set the\n                           <span class=\"ph uicontrol\">Width</span> and <span class=\"ph uicontrol\">Depth</span> (Height)\n                        properties.</p>\n<figure class=\"fig fignone\" id=\"xkf1665702809265__fig_d12995e1_d12996e1_d12997e1\"><figcaption><span class=\"fig--title-label\">Figure 1. </span>Help Text Editor</figcaption>\n<img alt=\"Define Help Text form\" class=\"image\" src=\"https://docs-be.rocketsoftware.com/bundle/uniface_104/page/definehelptexts.png?_LANG=enus\"/>\n</figure>\n</div>\n</li>\n</ol>\n</li><li class=\"li step stepexpand\" id=\"xkf1665702809265__li_d6230e1_d6231e1_d6232e1\">\n<span class=\"ph cmd\">To delete a help text, select the help text and choose <span class=\"ph menucascade\"><span class=\"ph uicontrol\">Edit</span><abbr title=\"and then\"> &gt; </abbr><span class=\"ph uicontrol\">Delete Help Text</span></span>. </span>\n</li><li class=\"li step stepexpand\" id=\"xkf1665702809265__li_d6233e1_d6234e1_d6235e1\">\n<span class=\"ph cmd\">To save new or modified help texts, choose <span class=\"ph menucascade\"><span class=\"ph uicontrol\">File</span><abbr title=\"and then\"> &gt; </abbr><span class=\"ph uicontrol\">Save</span></span>. </span>\n</li><li class=\"li step stepexpand\" id=\"xkf1665702809265__li_d6236e1_d6237e1_d6238e1\">\n<span class=\"ph cmd\">To call a Uniface help text:\n </span>\n<div class=\"itemgroup info\">\n<ol class=\"ol\" type=\"a\">\n<li class=\"li\" id=\"xkf1665702809265__li_d6239e1_d6240e1_d6241e1\">Use the <span class=\"keyword cmdname\">help</span> and <span class=\"keyword cmdname\">$text</span> ProcScript commands to specify the help text to be called.\n </li>\n<li class=\"li\" id=\"xkf1665702809265__li_d6242e1_d6243e1_d6244e1\">Ensure that the appropriate language and library are defined for the help text, either in ProcScript or in the assignment file.\n </li>\n</ol>\n<div class=\"code-toolbar\"><pre class=\"pre language-plaintext\" tabindex=\"0\"><code class=\"language-plaintext\">trigger help\n $variation = myapp\n $language = usa\n help $text(HLP523)\nend; help</code></pre><div class=\"toolbar\"><div class=\"toolbar-item\"><button class=\"copy-to-clipboard-button\" data-copy-state=\"copy\" type=\"button\"><span>Copy</span></button></div></div></div>\n</div>\n</li></ol></section>\n</div>\n</article></main></article>\n</div></div><div class=\"contentPlaceholder\" style=\"height: 500px;\"><div class=\"contentContainer zDocsSideBoxes\"><div><h5 aria-level=\"5\" class=\"css-g931ng\">Related Links</h5><ul><li><a class=\"css-ettsdk\" href=\"/de-DE/bundle/uniface_104/page/hir1705568318852.html\" stylesprops=\"[object Object]\"><svg aria-hidden=\"true\" class=\"ico-related-link\"><use xlink:href=\"#ico-related-link\"></use></svg>Messages</a><p>Messages are language-related objects that enable you to deploy a Uniface application in different languages and locales. They are stored in language-specific libraries, and Uniface automatically chooses the appropriate library at runtime based on the configuration.</p></li><li><a class=\"css-ettsdk\" href=\"/de-DE/bundle/uniface_104/page/zks1720074466587.html\" stylesprops=\"[object Object]\"><svg aria-hidden=\"true\" class=\"ico-related-link\"><use xlink:href=\"#ico-related-link\"></use></svg>help</a><p>Display help information, either a Uniface help message or information from the native help system.</p></li><li><a class=\"css-ettsdk\" href=\"/de-DE/bundle/uniface_104/page/xtf1665702608323.html\" stylesprops=\"[object Object]\"><svg aria-hidden=\"true\" class=\"ico-related-link\"><use xlink:href=\"#ico-related-link\"></use></svg>$text</a><p>Return the text of a message or help text.</p></li><li><a class=\"css-ettsdk\" href=\"/de-DE/bundle/uniface_104/page/rja1665702608398.html\" stylesprops=\"[object Object]\"><svg aria-hidden=\"true\" class=\"ico-related-link\"><use xlink:href=\"#ico-related-link\"></use></svg>$textexist</a><p>Return an indication of whether the specified message or help text exists.</p></li></ul></div></div></div></div><div class=\"bottomFeedback\"><div aria-labelledby=\"bottomFeedbackText\" class=\"bottomFeedbackContent\" role=\"group\"><span class=\"bottomFeedbackText\" id=\"bottomFeedbackText\">Was this topic helpful?</span><div class=\"bottomFeedbackButtonGroup\"><a data-backdrop=\"static\" data-target=\"#feedbackModal_bottom_5831135\" data-toggle=\"modal\" href=\"#\" role=\"button\" type=\"button\"><svg aria-hidden=\"true\" class=\"ico-thumbs-up\"><use xlink:href=\"#ico-thumbs-up\"></use></svg><span>Like</span></a><a data-backdrop=\"static\" data-target=\"#feedbackModal_bottom_5831135\" data-toggle=\"modal\" href=\"#\" role=\"button\" type=\"button\"><svg aria-hidden=\"true\" class=\"ico-thumbs-down\"><use xlink:href=\"#ico-thumbs-down\"></use></svg><span>Dislike</span></a></div></div></div><div style=\"position: fixed; bottom: 170px; right: 70px; cursor: pointer; transition-duration: 0.2s; transition-timing-function: linear; transition-delay: 0s; z-index: 3; opacity: 0; visibility: hidden; transition-property: opacity, visibility;\"><button aria-label=\"Scroll to top\" class=\"zDocsScrollTopBtn\" data-tooltip-content=\"Scroll to top\" data-tooltip-id=\"zDocsBackToTopToolTip\" id=\"zDocsScrollToTop\" type=\"button\"><svg aria-hidden=\"true\" class=\"ico-next\"><use xlink:href=\"#ico-next\"></use></svg></button></div></body></html>", "text": "Working with Help Texts Add to My Topics Add selected topic and subtopics Add Topic & Subtopics with topic head Add entire publication Watch Download PDF Save selected topic Save selected topic and subtopics Save entire publication Share Email Link Copy Link Feedback Last Updated Jan 19, 2024 Summarize Uniface 10.4 Working with Help Texts Define help texts to create large blocks of text that can be displayed in a Uniface help window. Note: Help texts are provided for backward compatibility. They are not recommended for modern applications. Open the help text editor: Choose More Editors > Help Texts . Select or create the Message Library in which you want to store the help texts. The object editor is now opened. To create a help text: Click New and enter the Help Name , Language , and optional Description . Note: Each help text must have a unique name. It cannot use the same name as a message because messages and help texts are stored in the same library. Enter the text in the Text field. Optionally, set the Window Geometry to define the position and size of the help window. To define the position, set the Left and Top properties. To define the dimensions, set the Width and Depth (Height) properties. Figure 1. Help Text Editor To delete a help text, select the help text and choose Edit > Delete Help Text . To save new or modified help texts, choose File > Save . To call a Uniface help text: Use the help and $text ProcScript commands to specify the help text to be called. Ensure that the appropriate language and library are defined for the help text, either in ProcScript or in the assignment file. trigger help $variation = myapp $language = usa help $text(HLP523) end; help Copy Related Links Messages Messages are language-related objects that enable you to deploy a Uniface application in different languages and locales. They are stored in language-specific libraries, and Uniface automatically chooses the appropriate library at runtime based on the configuration. help Display help information, either a Uniface help message or information from the native help system. $text Return the text of a message or help text. $textexist Return an indication of whether the specified message or help text exists. Was this topic helpful? Like Dislike"}